   <narrative xml:lang="EN">REE-CALL - Food Security, Resilience and Adaption Project (BGD-0010)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Bangladesh Rural (REE-CALL) Resilience project&#xA0; aims to strengthen community resilience in disaster-prone rural and urban areas of Bangladesh under four thematic areas: disaster preparedness; gender equality and women&#x2019;s leadership; economic empowerment; and water, sanitation and hygiene.&#xA0;&#xA0;This phase of the project&#xA0;focuses on influencing decision-makers in government and the private sector (from local to national levels) to ensure the rights&#xA0;of community members in climate change affected areas are fulfilled.</narrative>
  </description>
